The three of us work together
at the same company.

91
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,440
So you're a firefighter.

92
00:03:52,523 --> 00:03:55,485
Your eyebrows look like eagle wings,
so I pegged you for a cop.

93
00:03:55,568 --> 00:03:57,070
Is that a cop thing?

94
