175
00:07:18,563 --> 00:07:20,481
Why'd you do that
while Woo-seok was sleeping?

176
00:07:21,649 --> 00:07:24,861
- What did I do to deserve this?
- Seriously, man.

177
00:07:25,528 --> 00:07:26,988
He was sound asleep.

178
00:07:27,071 --> 00:07:29,031
He could have at least had
another half hour…

179
00:07:32,702 --> 00:07:33,995
Did you sleep well?

180
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:36,622
I wouldn't say I slept well, but I slept.

181
00:07:37,790 --> 00:07:40,376
The three of them snored so loudly
last night.

182
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:43,504
- So I heard.
- You don't snore, Woo-seok?

183
00:07:43,588 --> 00:07:45,131
Not really, no. But…

184
00:07:45,715 --> 00:07:47,341
You don't snore at all?

185
00:07:47,425 --> 00:07:48,968
