200
00:08:22,043 --> 00:08:23,544
- The coffee goes with this.
- Uh-huh.

201
00:08:24,128 --> 00:08:26,255
- So the pour over?
- That sounds better.

202
00:08:26,339 --> 00:08:28,549
Feels like we're living in the mountains.

203
00:08:29,884 --> 00:08:32,386
I look like the owner of this place,
don't I?

204
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:35,515
If we're gonna have
to get up early to greet the guests…

205
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:38,100
