206
00:08:38,184 --> 00:08:39,519
So you want a cup?

207
00:08:39,602 --> 00:08:41,896
Ah, man, this is the best.

208
00:08:42,772 --> 00:08:44,690
It's like a five-star hotel.

209
00:08:46,317 --> 00:08:48,486
Can't you stay through tomorrow morning?

210
00:08:48,945 --> 00:08:50,279
THINKING OUT LOUD
FOR ALL TO HEAR

211
00:08:50,363 --> 00:08:52,698
- Gosh…
- <i>Oppa</i>, put this over there for me.

212
00:08:52,782 --> 00:08:54,492
- Right.
- Thank you.

213
00:08:54,575 --> 00:08:55,660
Put it down there for me.

214
00:08:55,743 --> 00:08:57,662
- Anywhere specific?
- Down there. Down there.

215
00:08:57,745 --> 00:09:00,289
- Down there. Down there!
- Oh, down here.

216
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:03,209
FIDGET

217
00:09:03,292 --> 00:09:04,919
PEEK

218
00:09:05,002 --> 00:09:08,631
Just down there. Down there! Down there!

219
00:09:08,714 --> 00:09:10,841
- Oh, over here?
- Below that!

220
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,720
SCARED

221
00:09:14,804 --> 00:09:17,306
You nearly met the old me
just now, didn't you?

222
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:19,517
- Uh-huh, yeah. I see you haven't changed.
- Mm-hmm.

223
00:09:23,813 --> 00:09:24,897
Wow.

224
00:09:24,981 --> 00:09:26,065
PRETTY COOL

225
00:09:26,857 --> 00:09:28,109
That smell.

226
00:09:28,192 --> 00:09:29,569
- Great, right?
- It's amazing.

227
00:09:29,652 --> 00:09:30,945
Yeah.

228
00:09:31,028 --> 00:09:32,071
Oh, wow.

229
00:09:33,322 --> 00:09:34,407
Whoa.

230
00:09:34,490 --> 00:09:35,908
What an aroma.

231
00:09:36,409 --> 00:09:38,119
Make me one that's mellow and nutty.

232
00:09:38,202 --> 00:09:39,579
