233
00:09:39,662 --> 00:09:40,871
They're all acidic?

234
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:42,957
- I'll make it nutty.
- Make it nutty for me.

235
00:09:44,083 --> 00:09:46,752
Wow, that scent is amazing,
the coffee scent.

236
00:09:47,503 --> 00:09:48,504
Ethiopia.

237
00:09:51,382 --> 00:09:52,508
Ethiopia?

238
00:09:52,592 --> 00:09:54,093
I don't know much about coffee,

239
00:09:54,176 --> 00:09:56,762
but I know the Ethiopian aroma
when I smell it.

240
00:09:56,846 --> 00:09:59,515
- You mean coffee that came from Ethiopia?
- Yeah.

241
00:09:59,599 --> 00:10:00,975
Are you sure?

242
00:10:01,684 --> 00:10:04,395
It's Ethiopian. Sheesh.
I mean, it's not like they grew it here.

243
00:10:06,981 --> 00:10:09,150
How's this, <i>hyung</i>? The concentration.

244
00:10:09,233 --> 00:10:10,318
Too strong for you?

245
00:10:10,401 --> 00:10:11,819
- Oh, it's good.
- Not too strong?

246
00:10:11,902 --> 00:10:13,112
It's nutty, right?

247
00:10:13,946 --> 00:10:16,157
